---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Breadcrumb from '../../../components/Breadcrumb.astro';
import EmergencyBanner from '../../../components/EmergencyBanner.astro';
---

<Layout title="Irregular Heartbeat — Dr Delhasse, Cardiologist" description="An irregular heartbeat may signal a conduction disorder. Find out when to consult a cardiologist." lang="en">

  <section class="hero-page">
    <div class="container">
      <Breadcrumb items={[{label:'Home', href:'/en'}, {label:'Symptoms', href:'/en/symptoms'}, {label:'Irregular Heartbeat'}]} />
      <h1>Irregular <span class="text-primary">Heartbeat</span></h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">When your smartwatch alerts you</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <EmergencyBanner lang="en" />

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container detail-content">
      <img src="/images/detail/rythme-cardiaque-irregulier.webp" alt="Irregular heartbeat consultation" class="detail-hero-img" />
      <img src="/images/svg/symptomes/Arritmia-1.svg" alt="Irregular heartbeat" class="detail-icon" />

      <p>An irregular heartbeat is characterised by a heart that beats in a disordered manner. It can be a sign of an underlying problem such as atrial fibrillation or another cardiac conduction disorder. Although some episodes may be benign, it is essential to consult a cardiologist for an accurate diagnosis and to determine the underlying cause, especially if you experience recurring symptoms such as palpitations, irregular beats or dizziness.</p>

      <p>In a world where smartwatches and other health devices allow us to monitor our heart rate in real time, it has become easier to detect these irregularities, even before experiencing significant symptoms. However, although these tools are useful, they do not replace medical expertise. An assessment by a cardiologist remains essential to properly evaluate your cardiac health.</p>

      <div class="detail-cta">
        <a href="/en/symptoms" class="btn btn--outline-dark">&larr; All symptoms</a>
        <a href="/en/contact" class="btn btn--primary">Book an appointment</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  .hero-page { background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-navy) 0%, #1a3d6d 100%); padding: 6rem 0 4rem; color: var(--color-white); }
  .hero-page h1 { color: var(--color-white); font-size: 2.75rem; }
  .hero-sub { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75); font-size: 1.15rem; margin-top: 1rem; }
  .detail-content { max-width: 800px; }
  .detail-icon { width: 80px; height: 80px; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .detail-hero-img { width: 100%; height: 300px; object-fit: cover; border-radius: 8px; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .detail-content p { font-size: 1.05rem; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: var(--color-gray); }
  .detail-cta { display: flex; gap: 1rem; margin-top: 3rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  @media (max-width: 768px) { .hero-page h1 { font-size: 2rem; } }
</style>
